headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Bikers of All Stripes Come Out Ahead This Week
content: Rebels who run criminal enterprises are thriving in their own ways: completing Document Forgery, Counterfeit Cash, and Weed MC Sell Missions will pay out double GTA$ until September 22. Resupply costs for all MC businesses are also halved, so your accountant is going to be working some serious overtime.
